  <brief_title>Validation of a Non-invasive Hemodynamic Monitor (NexFin) in Pregnant Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of Non-invasive Monitoring of Blood Pressure and Cardiac Output in Healthy Pregnant Women During Cesarean Section</official_title>
  <sponsors>
